hopobject.body: I have my own business icon meals free shipping By the end of the year Google Glass aims to be a fully functional wearable computer that lets you surf the web, post on Facebook, reply to email, and do everything your smartphone would do, all without having to pull your phone out of your pocket. That functionality will come in the form of apps written for its Android based operating system, which has already proven capable of supporting such apps on phones and tablets.
